{"tid":1216175,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中 大 校 長 段 崇 智 公 開 信","createTime":"2019-06-13T09:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T11:37:19.000Z","uid":143210,"like":2,"dislike":93,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"41cba4b0b4f9d15afe2beb5f2ea50da5c32bac76","tid":1216175,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:15:13.000Z","msg":"各位同學:<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n對於近日發生的事件，尤其知道有中大同學在事件中受傷及被捕，我和同事們都十分關注及擔憂。我呼籲各位同學千萬要確保自身和他人的安全，遠離危險的地方。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n我們會繼續與同學保持聯絡及溝通，你們的平安從來都是我們作為師長至為關心的。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n我深切盼望各方能保持冷靜和克制，重回理性的討論，讓事件得以妥善解決。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n校長<br />\n段崇智<br />\n二零一九年六月十三日<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n13 June 2019<br />\nDear<br />\nStudents,<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nI<br />\nam writing to express the deep concern shared by myself and my colleagues over<br />\nthe recent incidents in Hong Kong, especially knowing that some of our students<br />\nhave been injured and detained.&nbsp; I strongly urge all students to avoid<br />\nhigh-risk sites, and pay heed to your own safety and that of others.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nWe<br />\nwill keep in close contact with our fellow students. Your well-being has been<br />\nand will always be our primary concern.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nIt<br />\nis my sincere wish that all members of the society will stay calm, and that the<br />\nmatter will be resolved with rational discussion.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nVery<br />\nsincerely,<br />\nRocky<br />\nS. Tuan<br />\nVice-Chancellor<br />\nand President"},{"pid":"c9e1c9f6d33ca90502c932801a598c19055bdbc3","tid":1216175,"uid":143210,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"段生係咪對象錯咗，應該呼籲嘅唔係呢邊啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f4a45c325640d0e3d7962afbb6c345e422732d","tid":1216175,"uid":143210,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:17:48.000Z","msg":"推畀大家睇下中大有幾中？<img src=\"/assets/face